Notes: UMR holds Truman to 26.7 percent shooting in posting its ninth win overall and
third MIAA victory in its final MIAA home contest...UMR takes the lead for
good by outscoring Truman 10-2 over the final 5:15 of the first half...UMR
posts its first season sweep of an MIAA opponent since 1999-00 (Washburn).
Game.Officials: John Murray,  Phil Griffin,  Tom Sullivan
